title: Don and Mike Show podcasts - year 2000
description:
This is the collected batch of podcasts of the now cancelled Don and Mike Show - year 2000 as found on donandmikewebsite.com

I plan to add years 2001-2008 (up until the final show)
This takes time, so I'll get it done when I get it done (though 2001 should be up by tomorrow)
If I ever get this finished, I might do earlier stuff - before 2000, that is, but I started with 2000 because that was the year I started listening.

If there are troubles with this upload, it's because I've never done it before and I'm an idiot. Thnx
